    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve honestly gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have absolutely babied this car, and it\u2019s in pristine condition inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in perfect shape, this is definitely the one for you. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out!",
      "price": 44500.0,
