      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been preserved in absolute showroom condition, exhibiting no cosmetic or mechanical compromises. Every surface remains pristine, reflecting a standard of maintenance reserved for the most discerning collectors. We invite serious inquiries to acquire this benchmark of excellence.",
      "price": 44850.0,
