      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this total gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in showroom-ready condition and has been pampered since day one\u2014it looks and feels just like it did when it first hit the road! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's completely flawless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and is ready for a new adventure, you've found it. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
