    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-tier condition. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated double-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis integrity is flawless, with no subframe fatigue or stress fractures. Every mechanical component, from the high-pressure VANOS lines to the suspension bushings, remains in peak operational status. This is a visceral, high-revving analog masterpiece that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment, offering a driving experience that mirrors its original factory delivery.",
